OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome bright or sunny spells
OL,6,Fthrough the day. There will be a few
OL,7,Fshowers but some spells of drier
OL,8,Fweather too. Fresh to strong
OL,9,Fnorthwesterly winds across Shetland at
OL,10,Ffirst.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPartly cloud this evening
OL,13,Fwith a few showers. Then the rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will see variable amounts of
OL,15,Fcloud and occasional showers. A cold
OL,16,Fnight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FAfter a mainly dry start rain
OL,19,Fwill spread southeastwards during the
OL,20,Fmorning, clearing from the north
OL,21,Fthrough the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
